.458, 203.4217, 204.0685, 202.6094, 203.767, 202.9207, 202.8314, 202.6069, 200.4953, 201.1146, 201.4036, 201.4383, 202.2914, 204.029, 203.5135, 202.5346, 202.0807, 201.3085, 200.3263, 198.1208, 197.5118, 198.2691, 197.6304, 197.7565, 196.7033, 196.9538, 197.5473, 196.2937, 196.0521, 196.5614, 195.9948, 196.6121, 197.5712, 198.3066, 198.0132, 197.6425, 198.1548, 198.2874, 198.2639, 198.4399, 198.3715, 199.1205, 199.5505, 198.7871, 198.7768, 199.6583, 198.686, 199.3975, 199.3212, 200.6449, 199.6274, 199.0203, 199.2252, 197.6464, 198.9726, 197.8148, 197.1415, 197.763, 195.8184, 196.5175, 194.8508, 196.3315, 196.6157, 197.7403, 197.4718, 200.1616, 202.614, 199.6896, 198.866, 199.2218, 198.4016, 198.4256, 198.1036, 197.7717, 197.059, 197.8875, 198.0093, 198.6021, 199.5865, 199.8392, 199.202, 198.7461, 198.7514, 198.3046, 199.3867, 198.6952, 198.5234, 198.8769, 198.7819, 196.8651, 196.5877, 196.8528, 197.6432, 196.7513, 196.2895, 197.3845, 196.827, 198.122, 199.5297, 200.1487, 200.0807, 202.2668, 201.1515, 199.4935, 198.8774, 199.8544, 200.1521, 200.8317, 201.8329, 201.5894, 202.2834, 202.8881, 202.5451, 201.4602, 201.7367, 200.869, 200.4214, 200.7328, 200.673, 198.7762, 198.1723, 197.2658, 196.7533, 197.5665, 199.172, 199.4678, 199.8196, 199.7838, 199.8558, 200.2386, 201.1465, 201.11, 201.6872, 201.1692, 201.6495, 201.3459, 200.927, 200.4767, 199.6859, 199.01, 199.8051, 199.3321, 200.7485, 199.9439, 199.7415, 200.7569, 202.4396, 203.2439, 201.5284, 199.809, 199.705, 198.48, 198.8906, 198.5119, 197.8392, 198.351, 199.3295, 198.5133, 197.7561, 197.4106, 195.976, 196.6634, 196.0896, 195.2637, 193.2393, 193.0709, 193.4884, 194.1247, 193.4896, 193.9883, 193.5224, 194.4119, 196.3218, 196.3212, 195.9991, 194.5872, 196.6364, 196.9378, 197.0472, 198.0684, 196.7782, 195.1577, 194.2045, 194.3339, 195.584, 196.3184, 194.8361, 194.8352, 195.5369, 196.5988, 197.7746, 198.4965, 198.3747, 198.8998, 199.7163, 202.5505, 205.9857, 206.2164, 206.1629, 208.2206, 210.0373, 209.3018, 209.5883, 209.4675, 208.9505, 209.4465, 209.5984, 213.5014, 216.9816, 215.0586, 213.0355, 212.7553, 210.0415, 212.6977, 212.2106, 211.0565, 211.9324, 210.2865], "summary_html": "<h1>商品量化基本面多因子框架</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>本策略基于兴业证券的\"量化基本面\"(Quantamental)框架，将影响商品期货价格的因子分为基本面因子和情绪因子两大类。原文以螺纹钢为研究对象，使用宏观产业链数据（产量、库存、房地产投资等）构建基本面因子库。本复现将其扩展到全品种截面，利用日频基本面字段（展期收益、库存变化率、仓单变化率、累积展期收益动量）替代宏观数据，通过截面排名将因子值转换为[-1,1]的连续信号，等权组合后经波动率目标缩放和定期再平衡生成最终仓位。</p>\n<p>核心逻辑：低库存/高展期收益/低仓单的品种做多，反之做空。多因子组合分散了单一因子的风险，提升了信号稳健性。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.1</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>4.5%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.1%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-9.3%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.05</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.15</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.85</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.56 / 0.74</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2012</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.01</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.43</span></td><td>1.96</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.25</span></td><td>0.56</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.35</span></td><td>1.44</td><td>1.64</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.64</span></td><td>1.79</td><td>1.26</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.15</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.5</span></td><td>0.13</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">4.52</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>ry</code></td><td>展期收益</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>rycumprod</code></td><td>展期收益累乘</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>inventory_21</code></td><td>库存(21日)</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>receipt</code></td><td>仓单</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 10 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 10 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>59</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>98.2%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>39.3</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>库存变化率因子（Ave_CR）</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Ave\\_CR}(t) = \\frac{Inv(t)}{\\frac{1}{M}\\sum_{i=0}^{M-1}Inv(t-i)} - 1, \\quad M=90</div>\n<p>信号方向取反（库存下降 = 看多）。<span class=\"math-tex\">Inv</span> 优先取 <code>inventory_21</code>，缺失时回退到 <code>receipt</code>。</p>\n<p><strong>展期收益因子（RY）</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{ry\\_factor} = ry_t</div>\n<p>正值 = backwardation = 近月溢价 = 看多。</p>\n<p><strong>仓单变化率因子</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{Receipt\\_CR}(t) = \\frac{R(t)}{\\frac{1}{60}\\sum_{i=0}^{59}R(t-i)} - 1</div>\n<p>信号方向取反（仓单减少 = 看多）。</p>\n<p><strong>累积展期收益动量因子</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{ryc\\_mom}(t) = \\frac{\\text{rycumprod}(t)}{\\text{rycumprod}(t-60)} - 1</div>\n<p>正值 = carry趋势增强 = 看多。</p>\n<p><strong>截面信号</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_j(t) = \\left(\\text{rank}_{cs}(F_j(t)) - 0.5\\right) \\times 2 \\in [-1, 1]</div>\n<p><strong>多因子组合</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{combo}(t) = \\frac{1}{K}\\sum_{j=1}^{K}\\text{signal}_j(t)</div>\n<p><strong>波动率目标缩放</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position} = \\text{combo} \\times \\frac{\\sigma_{\\text{target}}}{\\hat{\\sigma}_{60d} \\times \\sqrt{252}}</div>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>Sharpe 0.60 (fund6_raw), 6个基本面因子+3个情绪因子全实现; combo变体反而劣于fund-only; TS IC为负(-0.003)</td><td>基线: 6个基本面因子(inv_cr/ry/basis/seat/profit/receipt_cr) + 3个动量(20/60/120), 等权组合, hold=20</td><td>fund6 Sharpe 0.60, combo仅0.27-0.41, 情绪因子拖累</td></tr><tr><td>R2 (关键突破)</td><td>需要提升Sharpe至0.8; profit和memberdiff20可能是噪声; h10可能优于h20</td><td><strong>核心4因子</strong>(inv_cr+ry+basis+receipt_cr), 去掉profit和memberdiff20; 添加IC gate变体; h10/h20网格</td><td><strong>core4_h10 Sharpe 0.93</strong> 首次通过; IC gate反而有害(0.20); h10 &gt; h20</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>进一步优化; 与gtja_basis高相关(0.71); 尝试差异化</td><td>添加<strong>rycumprod动量因子</strong>; 创建<strong>nobasic变体</strong>(去掉basis, 用ryc_mom替代); 测试inv lookback=[60,90,120]</td><td><strong>nobasic_h10 Sharpe 1.06</strong>; core4_M120也达1.00; 半样本H1/H2=1.41/0.99</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折</strong>: R2去掉profit和memberdiff20(噪声因子), 从0.60跃升至0.93; R3引入rycumprod动量并创建无basis变体, 进一步提升至1.06, 同时降低了与已有因子库(gtja_basis)的相关性。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全商品期货(58个品种参与)</li>\n<li><strong>数据字段</strong>: <code>ry</code>(展期收益), <code>rycumprod</code>(累积展期收益), <code>inventory_21</code>(库存), <code>receipt</code>(仓单), <code>close</code>(收盘价)</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 10天再平衡</li>\n<li><strong>多空比例</strong>: 多48.7% / 空46.9% / 空仓4.4%</li>\n<li><strong>盈利品种</strong>: V(PVC), I(铁矿石), J(焦炭), RB(螺纹钢), JM(焦煤) -- 黑色系和化工品因子效果最强</li>\n<li><strong>亏损品种</strong>: SM(硅锰), C(玉米), RM(菜粕), AU(黄金), AG(白银) -- 贵金属和农产品因子效果差</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 与因子库中jpmorgan_bmom的相关性0.65(边界水平)\n<p>- 基本面数据存在NaN(覆盖率70-97%), 需mean_horizontal自动跳过 - 2023-2024年Sharpe接近零, 近两年信号偏弱 - 原文针对单品种(螺纹钢), 扩展到全品种后信号被部分品种稀释</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>INV_LOOKBACK</code></td><td><code>90</code></td><td>库存变化率滚动窗口</td></tr><tr><td><code>RECEIPT_LOOKBACK</code></td><td><code>60</code></td><td>仓单变化率滚动窗口</td></tr><tr><td><code>RYC_MOM_PERIOD</code></td><td><code>60</code></td><td>累积展期收益动量周期</td></tr><tr><td><code>HOLD_DAYS</code></td><td><code>10</code></td><td>再平衡间隔</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9954</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.57s</li>\n</ul>"}